  <brief_title>Black Cohosh Extract for the Management of Moderate to Severe Menopausal Symptoms in Thai Women</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cimicifuga Racemosa Rhizome and Root Extract for the Management of Moderate to Severe Menopausal Symptoms in Thai Women: a Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
