  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Cimicifuga racemosa (black cohosh) rhizome and root extract have been used to treat
      menopausal symptoms. To date, there are still scarce information about its efficacy in Thai
      women with menopausal symptoms. The purpose of this study will assess the efficacy of black
      cohosh extract in management of menopausal symptoms in Thai women.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
